channel.title: Was fast, now slow?
channel.description: Hey guys, whenever my cache downloads to my client, it's incredibly slow. It was pretty fast yesterday like, I could to 3 and it's at 1, I count to 3 it's at 2, and so on. I stopped the download and came back to it today and whenever I try it, it's like, 1, count to eleven, 2 count to 20, and it just keeps getting slower and eventually just plain stops, any help?
